Class EventImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.google.wave.api.impl.EventImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Event
public class EventImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Event

The Event implementation that wraps an underlying EventData object and can traverse wavelets and blips if available in the message bundle.

Author:
scovitz@google.com (Seth Covitz)
